These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, mirinda, water
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, prince, davidoff, swisher
1. the baccarat-smoker is somewhere to the left of the davidoff-smoker##5
2. the person drinking lemonade is not the baccarat-smoker##6
3. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
6. the baccarat-smoker is not the person drinking mirinda##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | lemonade   | water    | juice    | mirinda |
| Sport      | swisher | baccarat | davidoff | prince |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, azalea, balloon-flower, iris
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, grapefruit, lettuce, onion
1. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsazalea is somewhere to the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
3. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the person who growsiris##5
4. the person who growsazalea is not the person eating grapefruit##6
5. the person eating onion is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
6. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
7. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growslily##1
8. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the left of the person who growslily##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | azalea  | balloon-flower    | lily | iris    |
| Food       | onion | grapefruit | lettuce  | artichoke |

