.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, spanish, nigerian, mexican
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, doctor, electrician, police-officer
1. the mexican is not the coach##6
2. the doctor is not the nigerian##6
3. the electrician is on the left or right of the spanish##3
4. the doctor is the canadian##1
5. the spanish is on the left of the doctor##1
6. the canadian is in an odd position##4
7. the coach is on the far left or far right##3
8. the electrician is somewhere to the left of the police-officer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | mexican       | spanish  | canadian  | nigerian |
| Job        | electrician | police-officer | doctor | coach  |

