.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, azure, ivory, aquamarine
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, colombian, indian, polish
1. the australian is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
2. the person who likes aquamarine is not the colombian##6
3. the australian is on the far right##1
4. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
5. the person who likes ivory is the person who likes ivory##1
6. the person who likes ivory is somewhere to the left of the australian##5
7. the person who likes ivory is somewhere to the left of the person who likes brown##5
8. the person who likes azure is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
9. the person who likes azure is somewhere to the left of the polish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | azure | ivory    | brown  | aquamarine   |
| Nationality   | indian  | polish | colombian | australian |

