.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, spy, time-travel, zombie
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk, sprite, lemonade
1. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
2. the person drinking sprite is not the person watching spy movies##6
3. the person watching documentary movies is the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
5. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
6. the person watching spy movies is the person drinking juice##1
7. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | spy     | time-travel | documentary |
| Music-Genre   | sprite | juice | lemonade      | soy-milk         |

