3. the social-worker is on the right of the journalist##1
4. the journalist is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
5. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left or right of the journalist##3
6. the coach is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
7. the person who growsaconite is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdaffodil##5
8. the person who growspoppy is not the social-worker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
