The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, helicopter, skateboard, subway
1. the oliveros-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the helicopter is not the old-henry-smoker##6
3. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the right of the havana-smoker##5
4. the person driving the subway is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
6. the person driving the subway is the havana-smoker##1
7. the oliveros-smoker is not the person driving the subway##6
8. the dunhill-smoker is somewhere to the right of the old-henry-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | oliveros  | havana | old-henry    | dunhill |
| Transport   | helicopter | subway | skateboard | airplane  |

