.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, hedgehog, rabbit
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, thai, mexican, american
1. the dutch is not the owner of the ferret##6
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the american is the american##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the american##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is not the american##6
6. the thai is not the owner of the fish##6
7. the american is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the hedgehog is the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | hedgehog | ferret        | rabbit  | fish     |
| Sport   | dutch     | american | thai | mexican |

