.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, fishing, rock-climbing, traveling
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, broccoli, kale, zucchini
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
2. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is chess##5
3. the person eating kale is not the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##6
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person eating zucchini and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
6. the person eating broccoli is between the person eating grapefruit and the person who's hobby is chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | fishing    | chess | traveling |
| Music-Genre   | grapefruit         | broccoli | zucchini   | kale     |

