4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person playing scrabble and the person who's sport is climbing##2
6. the person playing scrabble is not the person who's sport is baseball##6
7. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job     | billiard  | backgammon | poker | scrabble |
| Sport   | baseball | climbing | cricket   | water-polo |

