.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-19::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, november, january, february
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, lizard, mouse
1. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the lizard##5
2. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5
3. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the owner of the mouse is not the person who's birthday is in may##6
5. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in november##2
6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
8. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | november | january | may | february |
| Pet     | lizard  | fish      | chinchilla  | mouse       |

